title: Radio Rental is Back Open!
description:
Great news! Radio Rental is open! Terry Carnation would like to welcome you back to the store on 4/29 for all new tapes, or get your fix 1 week early as a Tenderfoot+ subscriber. For exclusive episodes, ad-free listening, and early access subscribe to Tenderfoot+ on Apple Podcasts or visit tenderfootplus.com.
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
